!!##NAME
!!    cher2(3f) - [BLAS:COMPLEX_BLAS_LEVEL2] A := A + alpha*CX*CONJUGATE-TRANSPOSE(CY)n + CONJUGATE(alpha)*CY*CONJUGATE-TRANSPOSE(CX);
