!!##NAME
!!    chpr(3f) - [BLAS:COMPLEX_BLAS_LEVEL2] performs the hermitian rank 1 operation
!! A := A + alpha*CX*CONJUGATE-TRANSPOSE(CX), a a (square) hermitian packed.
!!
!!##SYNOPSIS
!!
!!     SUBROUTINE CHPR(UPLO,N,ALPHA,X,INCX,AP)
!!
!!       .. Scalar Arguments ..
!!       REAL,intent(in)       :: ALPHA
